summary: An Candy Shop Addition To Windhelm City
descriptionHtml:
[font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]This mod adds an Candy Store at Windhelm,at the entrance of Gray Quarters.There are all sorts of candies.
All that you see displayed is static and thus by cannot be stolen,but if you speak with Gordana,who owns the store
you will see that she sells all those candies displayed.
Every Candy has its own property and reasonable price.
